These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, frog, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk | juice    | lemonade       |
| Pet         | goldfish | dog    | frog      | ferret |
| Transport   | ship   | car | roller | motorbike        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, eggplant, blueberry, mango
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, coach, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, tram, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the engineer##1
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the coach is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the accountant##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry   | eggplant | lime     | mango      |
| Job         | librarian | coach | engineer | accountant |
| Transport   | subway    | quad-bike   | tram     | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, fishing, cooking, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, gospel, funk, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, italian, spanish, japanese
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the fan of funk##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the japanese is on the right of the spanish##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | chess | fishing | cooking | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | gospel    | trance | funk     |
| Nationality   | indian | spanish    | japanese | italian    |

