.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, librarian, police-officer, chef
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, biathlon, cricket, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, car, bus, trike
1. the police-officer is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the librarian is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is the police-officer##1
7. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
8. the chef is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | lawyer | chef | police-officer | librarian |
| Sport       | biathlon     | weightlifting      | golf     | cricket      |
| Transport   | car | skateboard         | trike      | bus        |

