.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, reading, sudoku, baking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, scientific, spy, adventure
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, volleyball, sailing
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | baking | reading  | fishing      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | family        | adventure  | scientific       |
| Sport         | parkour | volleyball    | soccer | sailing |

