.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, dressmaker, project-manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, epic, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, classical, punk
1. the electrician is the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of punk##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
5. the freelancer is on the far left##1
6. the person watching epic movies is the dressmaker##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the project-manager is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | freelancer | dressmaker | project-manager | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | epic  | action | time-travel   |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | soul     | classical | hip-hop       |

