.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, corn, carrot, banana
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, rock-climbing, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, fantasy, adventure
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
2. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is the person eating carrot##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | watermelon  | banana | carrot   | corn     |
| Hobby         | traveling | photography   | chess  | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy         | scientific  | horror | adventure  |

