.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, tea, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, musical, scientific, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, spanish, indonesian
1. the person drinking cola is the spanish##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the indonesian is the person drinking tea##1
7. the brazilian is on the left of the indonesian##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | tea     | mirinda | cola |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | family | scientific       | musical    |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | indonesian | japanese    | spanish |

