.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, raspberry, zucchini, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, techno, rock, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, rugby, basketball, climbing
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | zucchini        | peach   | raspberry  | kiwi   |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | gospel     | techno    | rock       |
| Sport         | rugby | surfing | basketball | climbing |

