.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, coffee, juice
There 4 different types of food: corn, raspberry, pear, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: pony, fish, horse, hamster
1. the person drinking juice is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person eating corn is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | coffee | juice | almond-milk        |
| Food       | cauliflower | corn  | raspberry | pear     |
| Pet        | fish    | horse   | hamster  | pony |

