.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, pilot, librarian, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, tennis, rowing, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, trike, quad-bike, taxi
1. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the pilot##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the coach##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | accountant  | coach | pilot  | librarian |
| Sport       | rowing | tennis        | basketball | ice-hockey       |
| Transport   | ship   | trike          | taxi          | quad-bike       |

