.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading, skydiving, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, western, satire, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, thai, nigerian
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the thai##1
7. the nigerian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | skydiving   | rock-climbing | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | epic | western   | animation |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | chinese  | thai  | dutch  |

