.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, cooking, dancing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, soul, d&b, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, basketball, weightlifting, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of soul##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | gardening | cooking    | singing        | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | soul     | d&b     | hip-hop        | techno   |
| Sport         | basketball   | golf | weightlifting | tennis  |

