.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, disaster, adventure, crime
There are 4 different nationalities: british, argentine, japanese, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, bus, scooter
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the japanese##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the german##1
3. the british is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
8. the argentine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | crime  | time-travel    | adventure    |
| Nationality   | german | japanese  | british  | argentine |
| Transport     | scooter  | tram | bus | airplane        |

