.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, 7up, fanta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, action, musical, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, cricket, ice-hockey, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person drinking milk is the person watching disaster movies##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk        | fanta    | almond-milk | 7up      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster        | thriller   | action  | musical  |
| Sport         | basketball | cricket | ice-hockey   | rugby |

