.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, argentine, indian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, baseball, lacrosse, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, trike, car, bus
1. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | argentine | indian | japanese |
| Sport         | baseball | soccer | swimming  | lacrosse  |
| Transport     | taxi  | trike | bus     | car  |

