.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, social-worker, freelancer, librarian
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, american, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the social-worker is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the freelancer##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
4. the american is on the far right##1
5. the chinese is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
7. the librarian is on the far right##1
8. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | social-worker  | freelancer  | electrician | librarian |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | chinese | colombian   | american      |
| Sport         | surfing | ice-hockey    | volleyball   | skateboarding         |

 